<P>
   CLINTON-DENIAL _ (Washington) _ The American public Monday
finally got President Clinton's long-delayed answer to a very
personal question. Now another question might be: Could this mess
all have been over seven months ago, almost before it even began?
By DAVID GOLDSTEIN. 30 inches. Story will move in the ``a''
