</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-WOMEN _ (Kansas City, Mo.) _ For better. For worse. For
seven months, many American women have stuck with President
Clinton. He may have broken his vows to his wife, they said, but he
was faithful to causes important to them. And at least some said
they did not care what Clinton told a grand jury Monday. They like
his policies; they want the investigation to be over. By JEAN
BUCHANAN AND MATTHEW SCHOFIELD. 27 inches. Story will run in the
