   BANK-STOCKS-MARKETPLACE (Undated) _ While the market as a whole
has taken a well-publicized drubbing since mid-July, many bank
stocks have been beaten down more brutally. The villains pulling
down bank stocks are varied and well-known, but the extent of the
damage has drawn less scrutiny. By Timothy L. O'Brien.
</P>
