points of view that have not prevented the Seattle couple from
planning to marry. And when the two 30-year-olds met after work
Monday evening and watched President Clinton speak from the White
House, both initially chose the same word to describe the address:
``embarrassing.'' But their words, it turned out, did not mean the
same thing. By Sam Howe Verhovek.
</P>
