<DOCNO> NYT19980818.0122 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-18 13:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9270 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LEVINGSTON-COLUMN-BOS     08-18 0648
