   ROUND-ROCK _ ROUND ROCK, Texas _ After more than a month of
voting in the contest to rename the minor-league baseball team
Nolan Ryan wants to bring to Round Rock, his son Reid announced the
new name. (Drum roll please.) And the winner is . . . The Round
Rock Express. (Davenport, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
