   EXCLUSIVE-CLINTON-LEWINSKY (Washington) _ A tantalizing hint
emerges that President Clinton may have tried to communicate with
Monica Lewinsky in recent weeks. 500 words. By James Bennet.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   Note also that CLINTON-POLL, skedded earlier, has been
eliminated and will exist only as a graphic to accompany the lede
story.
</P>
