<HEADLINE>
INDIA TAPS INTO ITS DIASPORA TO SELL BONDS 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION WARNING: The following story is also being sent with
an `a' category code) 
 (bl)  
 By SOMINI SENGUPTA   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
